By Vanessa Obioha The governor of Oyo State, Seyi Makinde, has lost his mother. At the Friesland Campina WAMCO webinar to launch the new Center for Nigerian Dutch Dairy Development (CNDDD), where he is expected to speak, his representative, Executive Adviser to the Governor on Agribusiness Debo Akande, disclosed that the governor’s mother, Abigail, died on Thursday morning. An official statement is yet to be released. Details later…